oji\" />"},{"pid":"1495c77b43d88bbfdb828603a63b1c0131dbf9a2","tid":742173,"uid":22068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:23:59.000Z","msg":"正吖喂，中美貿戰燒埋香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1637b362994a1771fad0c1cfdca4f61781052156","tid":742173,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:31:09.000Z","msg":"蚛蟈或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"cc8933f48c3e26f69c6ee5df0cb1e2bddadd93ed","tid":742173,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:33:27.000Z","msg":"維護香港國際地位<br />\n係美國香港政策法"}]}